Here are some highlights about ASH governance since it was established in 1887. 🧵 1/5
https://t.co/KcVz7xeIqi

The State Hospital opened in January 1887. It was operated as an independent entity reporting to the governor until February 1941 when the 'State Hospital Board' was established. 

That 5 member board oversaw the operation of ASH from 1941 until 1974. 2/5
https://t.co/KcVz7xeIqi

SB1716 solves a long-time conflict created by the fact that @AZDHS both runs & regulates ASH [never a good governance model].

https://t.co/8reSZ1uS5J
